modules.description: Converts between Pascal, Camel, Snake, and Kebab case strings by inserting or removing underscores and hyphens and adjusting capitalization. Handles strings with mixed case and numeric characters, preserving original structure where possible. Transforms "JohnDoe" to "john_doe" and "john_doe" to "JohnDoe" with consistent casing rules.

Converts between Pascal, Camel, Snake, and Kebab case strings by adjusting capitalization and inserting or removing separators. Handles mixed-case and numeric strings while preserving original structure. Operations include transforming "JohnDoe" to "john_doe" and "john_doe" to "JohnDoe." Supports consistent casing rules across various input formats.
